"Xavass-e āyāt" (on the (magical) propertics of the Qor'an verses) from 1234 H. [1818 CE].
The text is 'Abd al-'Alī b. Moh. b. Hosayn's Persian translation of the Arabic orginal from 926 H. [1520 CE].
